data.description:
Location, Location, Location.  Imagine making this gorgeous home your own. Open floor concept. Upon entry enjoy beautiful, gleaming hardwood floors. Full of natural light throughout the common area. Formal dining room.  Corian countertops in kitchen. Upgraded with several new SS appliances and new fixtures. New hot water heater. 
Spacious primary bedroom on main with walk-in closet. En-suite with his and her sinks. Split bedroom concept. Upstairs bedroom has private, full bath. Perfect for guests. Sunroom w/ direct access to deck. Wooded backyard view. In-ground 6-zone irrigation system.  Low SC taxes.  Award-winning Fort Mill schools. Quick access to Charlotte, surrounding cities, shopping, and recreation.  The current owner's mortgage is VA loan and is ASSUMABLE by another veteran with their VA certificate. Assumable Rate is: 2.875%.
Washer and dryer convey with an acceptable offer.
